  "text": "The Lorenz orbits can be computed using a special method described in [CITATION_1] . Turbulence trajectories are obtained using ordinary direct numerical simulation, and to obtain a reliable comparison the Lorenz orbits too were computed using numerical integration. There is one important point pertinent to direct numerical simulation, however. The time-steps must be constant.",
